I need to identify the tax-related line item in the balance sheet that shows accrued but not yet paid taxes.

Looking at the balance sheet, I can see a line item called "Taxes Payable" which represents taxes that have been accrued but not yet paid. This is exactly what I'm looking for.

From the balance sheet:
- The initial amount for "Taxes Payable" as of 2023-12-31 is 0.00
- The end amount for "Taxes Payable" as of 2024-02-01 is 41840.70

These values represent the tax liability that has been recorded but not yet paid to tax authorities at the beginning and end of the reporting period.

```json
{"solution": {'initial value': '0.00', 'end value': '41840.70'}}
```
